    "Name": "Hermit Crab HMC-13",
    "Details": "The Hermit Crab doesn't make use of many advanced technologies, eschewing an XL Engine or Endo Steel for a standard fusion plant and chassis. In fact the only advanced technology is found in the ten double heat sinks and ER Medium Lasers it carries into combat. Though larger, heavier and less efficient than many similar systems, the reliance on simple, proven technology makes the Hermit Crab popular on Periphery worlds and with military commands. The engine powers it to a top speed of 118 km/h and seven jump jets allow it to cover 210 meters.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
